{
  "texts": [
    "-Furthermore, providing detailed metadata with the datasets significantly improves the finetuning process by offering valuable information for data preprocessing and the models to fine-tune with.",
    "Consequently, we select datasets for fine-tuning and evaluation based on these criteria collectively to facilitate effective model development and accurate evaluation.-Fine-tuning Dataset.",
    "In order to investigate the performance of federated fine-tuning with LLMs using private industrial data in real-world scenarios, we employ a private industrial dataset TutorCode [101] as the fine-tuning dataset in our study to satisfy real-world conditions to validate the effectiveness of federated fine-tuning.",
    "TutorCode is a curated collection of programming submissions sourced from the online programming education platform by 20 experts, ensuring integrity and quality by manual verification.",
    "To prevent data leakage, the dataset is not crawled from public repositories but collected from the company's proprietary data."
  ]
}